{"tid":1898262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【應該每人派一毛】陳茂波：窮，不會談忠心 !","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T04:45:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"066c56f9e85d9501461702e3ff1643d7c58a17ba","tid":1898262,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:33:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>為一毫子帶白粉<br />\n向上爬脫貧<br />\n陳茂波：窮，不會談忠心 !</strong><br />\n<br />\n10年前，《壹週刊 非常人語》訪問了當時的會計師公會主席，出爐選委陳茂波，他道盡半生向上爬的故事，半生追逐金錢，摯親一個個病故離去。<br />\n<br />\n沒有無緣無故的惡，他為何會變成劏房波囤地波？性格，或許真的決定命運。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n爬上了，又如何 ?（875期《壹週刊 非常人語》）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_469965_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_469965_0&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6Xw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=0c8fc84d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_469965_0&h=2217796f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_469965_0</a>"},{"pid":"dbddd4fd4139b9b581c55e7471470775d2aa6451","tid":1898262,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"勵志故事"},{"pid":"6857139aaf54eb864b9285d4491b4bf942409c85","tid":1898262,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"劏出彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c5c960765af4e0c194bb8e561aa1d98c85f1aa","tid":1898262,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"睇下支國富豪, 有錢既移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}